      "content": "For a truly sophisticated global look, the standard is impeccable tailoring and understated quality. Think well-fitting, neutral-toned garments made from quality fabrics, avoiding anything overly flashy or trendy. Polished means shoes are always clean and maintained, and grooming is meticulous—hair neat, nails tidy. Conversely, looking less professional involves loud logos, overly casual wear like ripped jeans or athletic gear, or any visible signs of sloppiness, which immediately signals a lack of respect for the setting.",
